{"tid":211803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla全球回收5.3萬架車","createTime":"2017-04-22T01:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T04:01:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f6409cb8459bf2b23d807cb244b57b1274d5c6","tid":211803,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T01:51:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19998074&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19998074%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170422&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23RjzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c7906d12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19998074%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170422&h=bd07a0f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19998074&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170422</a><br />\n<br />\nTesla全球回收5.3萬架車<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n部份去年生產的Model X須全球回收。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國電動車生產商Tesla宣佈全球召回5.3萬架Model S及Model X。該批電動車於2016年2月至10月期間生產，因當中一件由第三方供應商生產的小型齒輪，可能在製造過程中出現問題，影響電動泊車制動系統（parking brakes）的運作，故需要回收並更換相關零件。<br />\n<br />\n齒輪破損　或無法開車倒車<br />\n<br />\nTesla香港發言人表示，所召回的車輛當中少於5%的車輛可能受影響，暫未能提供香港要召回車輛的數字。若該齒輪破損，泊車後制動系統可能會出現無法鬆開的情況，並導致車輛無法開車及倒車，但強調相關零件不會對煞車系統造成任何運作上的影響，相信不會對車主和乘客構成安全問題；目前亦無錄得任何因此所致的意外或受傷事故，故仍能安全使用，但為安全起見，故決定主動為車輛更換有關零件。<br />\n受影響的車主會收到警示，提醒泊車制動需要接受維修保養，Tesla會在短期內向車主郵寄官方召回通知，更換相關零件需時約45分鐘，預料今年10月前能為所有受影響車輛更換零件。<br />\n■記者李詠希"},{"pid":"91ad56e2497ad49977b97c3937dbbcabaec7d0f0","tid":211803,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T03:15:08.000Z","msg":"第三方係咪支那呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526b1e77890f84e030d74587b22c8e2fa31838f0","tid":211803,"uid":15453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T04:01:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第三方係咪支那呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}